data.description: Gorgeous newer property located in a family oriented neighborhood in one of the fastest growing cities in US, Lehigh Acres. Built in 2022 boasting 1700 sq ft will easily accomodate any family with many upgrades and meticulously maintain by current owners. Tile troughout, kitchen with natural stone counter tops, SS appliances and much more, room for all your toys at 0.26 acres. Great for first time home buyers and investors alike, Make your appoitnment today!!!
